\ul\b Atat\'fcrk Hisseleri:\ulnone\b0  31 Aral\'fdk 2024 itibar\'fdyla T\'fcrkiye \'dd\'fe Bankas\'fd\rquote n\'fdn ortakl\'fdk yap\'fds\'fd \'feu \'feekilde: \par
